<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٧:</span> <span class="c3">{الحُطَمَةُ}</span>: اسْمُ النَّارِ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">مِثْلُ:</span> <span class="c3">{سَقَرَ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> , وَ <span class="c3">{لَظَى}</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
